    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="结构伪类选择器"><a href="#结构伪类选择器" class="headerlink" title="结构伪类选择器"></a>结构伪类选择器</h2><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">ul</span> <span class="selector-tag">li</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:first</span>-child&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:nth-child</span>(<span class="number">2</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:nth-of-type</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第一种选中了ul的第一个子元素，且该子元素的标签是li，如果是别的标签就不生效。同时也可使用last-child选择最后一个元素，标签不一样则不生效。</p><p>第二种先定位到父元素，再选择当前的第二个元素，如果不是p标签就失效。</p><p>第三种选中父元素，再选中其下的p元素中的第一个。</p><h2 id="属性选择器"><a href="#属性选择器" class="headerlink" title="属性选择器"></a>属性选择器</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a[id]&#123;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>选择存在id属性的元素</p><p>标签名 属性名&#x3D;属性值</p><p>&#x3D; 绝对等于 *&#x3D;包含这个元素 ^&#x3D;以这个开头 $&#x3D;以这个结尾</p><h2 id="字体样式"><a href="#字体样式" class="headerlink" title="字体样式"></a>字体样式</h2><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-tag">p</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">font</span>: italic <span class="number">500</span> <span class="number">30px</span> 华文行楷 ;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/*连写格式要求，字体大小必须保留，字体必须选一个，其他可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  有严格的顺序要求，先整体格式，再粗细，再字体大小，最后字体格式*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-tag">p</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">font-family</span>: 华文行楷,<span class="string">&quot;Microsoft Himalaya&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/*存在多种字体时从左往右优先级递减，电脑上没有华文行楷才会用下一个*/</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用font属性时，必须按照上面语法格式中的顺序书写，不能更换顺序，并且各个属性间以空格隔开。不需要设置的属性可以省略(取默认值)，但必须保留font-size 和font-family属性，否则 font 属性将不起作用。</p><h2 id="文本样式"><a href="#文本样式" class="headerlink" title="文本样式"></a>文本样式</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-css"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="selector-class">.p1</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">font-family</span>: 华文行楷;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">font-size</span>:<span class="number">30px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">63</span>, <span class="number">210</span>, <span class="number">210</span>, <span class="number">0.7</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="comment">/*最后的那个用来控制透明度*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">text-align</span>: center;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="comment">/*文本居中，text-align用来控制文本对齐方式*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="selector-tag">p</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:nth-of-type</span>(<span class="number">2</span>)&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">text-indent</span>:<span class="number">2em</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">background</span>: beige;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">height</span>:<span class="number">100px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="number">100px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="comment">/*text-indent控制缩进*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="comment">/*background用于设置背景，当背景高度和line-height一样时，字体居中*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="selector-tag">a</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">color</span>: red;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">        <span class="attribute">text-decoration</span>: none;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="comment">/*text-decoration 装饰 underline下划line-through中划 overline上划</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"><span class="language-css">    还可使用none来去除a标签本来下面有的下划线*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还有vertical-align用于水平对齐，要选择两个标签 a，b，对齐用middle。一般用于将图片和文字进行水平对齐。</p><h2 id="超链接伪类"><a href="#超链接伪类" class="headerlink" title="超链接伪类"></a>超链接伪类</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-css"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  <span class="selector-tag">a</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">text-decoration</span>: none;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="built_in">rgb</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  <span class="selector-tag">a</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css"><span class="comment">/*a:hover制作出鼠标悬停在该超链接时样式的变化，本示例中做出了萌娘百科的效果*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>事实上用hover就行，什么标签都可以。</p><p>建议使用span框起文本再hover来实现简单的隐藏文本。</p><h2 id="列表样式"><a href="#列表样式" class="headerlink" title="列表样式"></a>列表样式</h2><p>list-style可以变更列表前面的点，用none可以直接删掉。</p><p>div标签 没有实际意义的标签，用来把块分隔开，并使用css进行加工</p><h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-css"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  <span class="selector-tag">div</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">1000px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">700px</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">border</span>: <span class="number">1px</span> solid red;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">    <span class="attribute">background-image</span>:<span class="built_in">url</span>(<span class="string">&quot;../../../resources/image/海辺の双子 62608184_p0.jpg&quot;</span>) ;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  <span class="comment">/* background-image url插入图片，或者直接用纯色填满*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  <span class="comment">/* background 颜色， url插入图片， 插入位置x，y， 重复样式，也可以分开写*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">      <span class="comment">/*background-repeat: no-repeat;*/</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">     <span class="comment">/*repeat-x水平平铺，-y竖直，no-repeat不平铺 */</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css">  &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-css"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用div来划分出块，指定长度和宽度。</p><p>border边界固定格式，1px solid(实线) 颜色</p><p>对background的设置，repeat的使用</p><h2 id="盒子模型及边框的使用"><a href="#盒子模型及边框的使用" class="headerlink" title="盒子模型及边框的使用"></a>盒子模型及边框的使用</h2><p class='item-img' data-src='C:\Users\19670\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221118160811285.png'><img src="C:\Users\19670\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20221118160811285.png" alt="image-20221118160811285"></p><p>盒子模型有外边矩margin，边框border和内边框padding，可以使用css来控制这三个属性，而最里面的content是html的内容。</p><p>默认情况下设置的width和height只是在设定里面的content的内容，而很多标签如<h>已经自带了margin等属性，故可以通过margin：0；来使得外边框不起作用。</p><p>盒子的宽度 &#x3D; 内容宽度 + 左填充 + 右填充 + 左边框 + 右边框 + 左边距 + 右边距<br>盒子的高度 &#x3D; 内容高度 + 上填充 + 下填充 + 上边框 + 下边框 + 上边距 + 下边距</p><p>margin-top：上边距<br>margin-buttom：下边距<br>margin-left：左边距<br>margin-right：右边距 </p><p>可以单独设置每一条边，也可以直接用一个margin来统一设置四条边。</p><p>margin：0，auto；实现了水平居中，但auto无法实现垂直居中，因为水平方向上自动填充了父元素，即盒子单独占一行，而竖直方向上没有。</p><p>padding设置内边框也是如此，但内边框与外边框不同，内边框可以设置背景颜色和图片。</p><p>border 1px solid red     dashed表示虚线</p><h2 id="浮动"><a href="#浮动" class="headerlink" title="浮动"></a>浮动</h2><p>块级元素：独占一行</p><p>行内元素：不独占一行</p><p>行内元素可以被包含在块级元素里面</p><p>使用display：inline-block  使得即在行内又有块的属性</p><h2 id="定位"><a href="#定位" class="headerlink" title="定位"></a>定位</h2><p>1.相对定位：position：relative；</p><p>相对于原来的位置进行指定的偏移，仍然在标准文档流中，原来的位置会被保留</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">top</span>:-<span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">left</span>:-<span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">bottom</span>:-<span class="number">10px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">right</span>:<span class="number">20px</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.绝对定位：position：absolute</p><p>如果有父级元素，则基于最近的已定位的父级元素的位置进行绝对定位。</p><p>如果没有，则基于boby或者html即浏览器的边框进行绝对定位。</p><p>3.固定定位：position：fixed</p><p>元素的位置相对于浏览器窗口是固定位置，即使窗口滚动它也不会移动。</p><p>页面中某些元素需要一直出现在某个地方。</p><p>4.z-index调整层级，默认是负一，越大越优先。</p>]]></content>
    
    
